learning_outcomes.en:
Student:
1. has gained experience as an instructor in conducting workshops;
2. is able to assess the age-appropriateness of workshop activities and, if necessary, adapt them to the specifics of the participants;
3. is able to find a suitable communication and instructional style taking into account the age of the participants and different behaviors;
4. has gained teamwork experience in preparing thematic events and conducting workshops;
5. is able to plan, carry out and analyze his / her internship activities.

learning_outcomes.et:
Üliõpilane:
1. on saanud kogemuse juhendajana töötubade läbiviimisel 
2. oskab hinnata töötubade tegevuste eakohasust ning vajadusel kohandada neid vastavalt osalejate eripäradele;
3. oskab osalejate vanust ja erinevaid käitumisviise arvestades leida sobiliku suhtlemis- ja juhendamisstiili;
4. suudab oma praktikategevusi planeerida, läbi viia, analüüsida.
